HEADWORD: Geologize
<hw>Ge*ol"o*gize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Geologized</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
